"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-olympics-paris-triathlon-pollution-river-b2588058.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  TheParis 2024Olympicstriathlonvenue lay empty as the men's race was postponed because ofconcerns over water qualityin the River Seine on Tuesday, 30 July.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training had been cancelledon Sunday and Monday and the men's race, which had been due to start at 8am local time on Tuesday, has been moved to Wednesday.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will take place at 10.45am local time after the women's race at 8am.\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday remains a contingency day if one or both of the races are unable to go ahead, a World Triathlon spokesperson said.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 818, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 0.9993465426180359, \"rank\": 0.0006538846677282509, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tests carried out in the Seine today revealedwater quality did not provide sufficient guaranteesto allow the event to be held,\\\" a statement read.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999066479044, \"rank\": 9.321405262770067e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Despite the improvement in the water quality levels, the readings at some points of the swim course are still above the acceptable limits.\\\"\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers spent more than a billion euros cleaning up the river to prepare for the Games, but organisers knew heavy rain in the days before a competition could cause the levels of the harmful bacteria E. Coli to rise.\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ParismayorAnne Hidalgoswam in the Seine before the Games started, fulfilling a promise she made in January as part of a broader effort to showcase the river's improved cleanliness.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1398, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.999999066479044, \"rank\": 9.321405262770067e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.9999980653452054, \"rank\": 1.519489801247742e-06, \"